<br>
Unlike bans, suspensions are temporary and are eventually lifted. However, like bans, there's no real road of appeal and all decisions are final, though I have read of extremely remarkabe circumstances where disciplinary decisions have been amended. Your best bet is to contact your Game Master, however, if I were you, I would simply wait it out.<br>
